{"tid":1922261,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"耿爽︰中方反對借病毒源頭問題搞政治污名化","createTime":"2020-03-12T12:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T15:21:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"7cbb74a63feea933c6320f738aba0aca57c3b506","tid":1922261,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1514072_1_L_20200312190049.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1514072_1_L_20200312190049.jpg&h=1f27c48b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在北京，中國外交部在例行記者會被問到，中方能否提供證據，以證明新型冠狀病毒並非源於中國，發言人耿爽說，關於病毒源頭的問題，是一個科學問題，需要聽取專業、科學的意見，中方反對借這個問題搞政治污名化。當前，新冠肺炎疫情已經成為全球性流行病。面對疫情，國際社會應該同心協力，而不應相互攻擊指責，這完全不具建設性。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽又說，中方抗疫的努力和所取得的積極成效，得到國際社會的廣泛支持和普遍讚譽。當前疫情在全球多處爆發並呈現蔓延態勢，已經成為全球性流行病。中方願同國際社會加強合作、攜手抗疫，爭取早日戰勝疫情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514072-20200312.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514072-20200312.htm&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=999a8272\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514072-20200312.htm&h=4681fce8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514072-20200312.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1a5f4cca0920beea55668cdb3e12aadf85bf0087","tid":1922261,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:46:53.000Z","msg":"耿爽又不爽了"},{"pid":"2669530db05060ad6776a0436591918bb4a226eb","tid":1922261,"uid":78243,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:51:18.000Z","msg":"哦<br />\n武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"fcd745092f9dee8df7a5f168090ad4114febbeaa","tid":1922261,"uid":28279,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日屈美國"}